<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idefea9e84-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s6710"><num value="6710">§ 6710.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary for each of the fiscal years 1991 through 1997, to carry out this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idefea9e85-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/101/624/tXXIV/s2412">Pub. L. 101–624, title XXIV, § 2412</ref>, <date date="1990-11-28">Nov. 28, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/4062">104 Stat. 4062</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/104/127/tVIII/s843">Pub. L. 104–127, title VIII, § 843</ref>, <date date="1996-04-04">Apr. 4, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/1170">110 Stat. 1170</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idefea9e86-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idefea9e87-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="idefea9e88-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">This chapter, referred to in text, was in the original “this title”, meaning title XXIV of <ref href="/us/pl/101/624">Pub. L. 101–624</ref>, <date date="1990-11-28">Nov. 28, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/4058">104 Stat. 4058</ref>, known as the Global Climate Change Prevention Act of 1990, which is classified principally to this chapter. For complete classification of title XXIV to the Code, see Short Title note set out under <ref href="/us/usc/t7/s6701">section 6701 of this title</ref> and Tables.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idefea9e89-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1996—<ref href="/us/pl/104/127">Pub. L. 104–127</ref> substituted “1997” for “1996”.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
